{"type": "article", "id": 12686, "title": "Hozuki Lantern 2.0 版本", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-28T07:28:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060002216Zw8sdgzHkSYTKiU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本户外品牌 Snow Peak 之前推出的 Hozuki 灯第一代的时候曾经得到大家的广泛关注，最近他们又推出了这个灯的 2.0 版本，仍然采用是挂钩和垂线的设计，圆滚滚的灯罩憨态可掬，灯光亮起来后，有普通模式，蜡烛模式和睡眠模式可以选择，满足不同情境下用户的需求，同时最大限度节省电力。这是<a href=\"http://snowpeak.com/products/hozuki-lantern-2?variant=3109323332\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261404110OtXH5zJPWgvMA1x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140412kHushdrVDiyCvxNn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140412YXUFRo2BvVe3gwZr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140413ayfSrVUiNXcGFQHM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140413HzqdyFe8OLJljPEt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140413zLwUQOWrRkj8tC0D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140414ZNpEi2oBwzFrGCAf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65359477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}